headline: Why the Smartest Investors Are Buying Philip Morris International Stock and Not Altria
summary: In some ways, Altria and Philip Morris International are tied at the hip.  Altria (NYSE: MO) is an iconic consumer staples maker that has shifted and changed over the years.  Philip Morris International (NYSE: PM) shares some of the storied history of Altria, but the smartest investors know that its business is better.
